        dc:description           "Figure 47. Living snails from Bau A Cyclophorus perdix borneensis (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 8753 Gunung Kapor B Platyrhaphe linita (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 9700 Gunung Doya C Stomacosmethis sadongensis (E. A. Smith, 1895) ME 8761 Gunung Kapor D Pincerna globosa (H. Adams, 1870) ME 8749 Lobang Angin. All not to scale." , "Figure 3. A Craspedotropis borneensis (Godwin-Austen, 1889) ME 839 Gunung Batu B Cyclophorus perdix borneensis (Metcalfe, 1851) ME 8921 Gunung Doya C Ditropopsis everetti (E. A. Smith, 1895) ME 835 Gunung Kapor." ;
